data.description: Live a Life of Luxury in this beautiful Southern Colonial. Over 2,000 Sq Ft finished! It’s decorated with taste and loaded with luxury:  Gleaming Hardwoods, Plush Carpets, Vaulted Ceilings, Upgraded Light Fixtures, and so much more.  The Kitchen has been renovated to include Stone/Tile Countertops, Stainless Steel Samsung Appliances, Grey/ 42” European Hung Cabinets, and a nice deep Stainless-Steel Sink.  There’s a half bath, on the main level, off the foyer. Upstairs there’s 4 large bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The Primary Suite is huge with vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, and French Doors leading to a Grand Bath.  The finished basement has a third full bath and room for a 5th bedroom!  There’s even space for the theater room you’ve always wanted. Store your favorite toys in the spacious 2 Car Garage. Bar-be-cue with friends and family on the large back deck, while watching the kids play in the huge, fenced backyard.  Neighborhood amenities include:  Access to private lakes for kayaking and fishing, Beach Access (Lake Monroe), Community Center, Swimming Pool, Large Multi-Purpose Sport Courts, Picnic Pavilions, A Boat Ramp (Lake Madison), and Hiking Trails.  Home is calling from Presidential Lakes.
